'''雅诗阁'''（{{lang-en|The Ascott}}）是[[凯德集团|凯德集团]]旗下酒店品牌和全资子公司。

==历史==
1984年8月14日成立于[[新加坡|新加坡]]，2005年11月22日成立[[雅诗阁公寓信托|雅诗阁公寓信托]]。2008年4月28日成为[[凯德集团|凯德集团]]旗下全资子公司，<ref>{{cite web |title=CapitaLand makes offer for rest of Ascott Group |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB119983123356275753 |website=wsj.com |access-date=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107160544/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB119983123356275753 |dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2020年在全球30多个国家180多个城市有酒店业务。<ref>{{cite web |title=Ascott Opens Record 7,500 Units And Signs Over 14,100 Units In 2019 To Boost Fee Income |url=https://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4096296.html |website=hospitalitynet.org |access-date=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110225821/https://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4096296.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Ascott Limited |url=https://www.hospitalitynet.org/organization/17006242/the-ascott-limited.html |website=hospitalitynet.org |access-date=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119090431/https://www.hospitalitynet.org/organization/17006242/the-ascott-limited.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
